Title: Permits the redaction of certain physician's names on birth certificates
Summary: Permits the redaction of certain physician's names on birth certificates when such physician's license to practice medicine has been surrendered or revoked by the office of professional medical conduct.
LawCode: Add ยง4134-a, Pub Health L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law, in relation to the redaction of certain physician's names on birth certificates
